 electronconv        y     flagelectron flag for application of electron conversion coefficient
 racap               n     flagracap    flag for radiative capture model
 ldmodelracap        3     ldmodelracap level density model for direct radiative capture
 upbend              y     flagupbend   flag for low-energy upbend of photon strength function
 psfglobal           n    flagpsfglobal flag for global photon strength functions only
 globalwtable        y flagglobalwtable flag for global average wtable value instead of 1.
 strengthjp          n   flagstrengthjp flag for J,P-dependent photon strength function
 gnorm               n     flaggnorm    flag to normalize PSF to average radiative width
 #
 # Pre-equilibrium
 #
